to do upstairs.

06:00.985 --> 06:04.489
-What's goin' on, Vince?
-Hi. Called you guys
in early, huh?

06:04.489 --> 06:06.574
Yeah. A gunshot victim
over at Bellevue.

06:06.574 --> 06:10.620
-What had the night watch
so occupied?
-Uh, double in Midtown,

06:10.620 --> 06:13.581
then someone threw shots
outside a nightclub
on Varick Street.

06:13.581 --> 06:17.543
-Oh, yeah? What was that about?
-Well, I, um, got one of the
guys in the coffee room.

06:17.543 --> 06:20.546
He sells sausages
out on the sidewalk,
just right outside the place.

06:20.546 --> 06:23.216
-And he told you--
-Well,

06:23.216 --> 06:27.428
but he's the only witness
I had leverage on, off of
no food handler's permit.

06:27.428 --> 06:30.848
But he didn't tell me dick.
What--What time were
the gunshots, Vincent?

06:30.848 --> 06:34.852
-3:30.
-SIMONE: See, our gunshot
victim got admitted at 3:45.

06:34.852 --> 06:37.980
-We probably oughta talk
to this guy, huh?
-No one said no one was hit.

06:37.980 --> 06:40.400
-Anyone say anyone was robbed?
-Definitely not.

06:40.400 --> 06:42.693
All I got was
some street asshole
throwing shots.

06:42.693 --> 06:45.780
Plus, no food permit
for the sausage guy.

06:45.780 --> 06:48.616
Uh,
what's this guy's name, Vince?

06:48.616 --> 06:50.618
-Uh, Lorenzo Sharp.
-SIMONE:
Oh, good.

06:50.618 --> 06:53.663
Yeah. Excellent.

06:53.663 --> 06:57.208
I want to tell you this:
I'm getting those
chest pains again.

06:57.208 --> 07:00.920
-Yeah, huh?
