and I tested abnormal.

07:08.428 --> 07:10.430
And I wanna tell you that now.

07:10.430 --> 07:13.099
-You gettin' pains right now?
-No, but I'm very upset.

07:13.099 --> 07:16.561
-Want someone to give you
a ride home? We'll take a ride.
-No. You go ahead.

07:16.561 --> 07:19.605
-I'm gonna go in a few minutes.
-Hey, you gotta take care of
yourself though, Vince, huh?

07:21.816 --> 07:25.695
-Poor bastard.
-Shows you can be stupid
and in bad health.

07:29.699 --> 07:33.494
I'm Detective Simone, Lorenzo.
This is Detective Sipowicz.

07:33.494 --> 07:36.581
Y'all drag me in here. Man, I'm
just tryin' to make a living.
I ain't hurtin' nobody.

07:36.581 --> 07:39.459
-All right. Don't go to pieces.
-We need to know what you saw
on the street before.

07:39.459 --> 07:41.878
Not a damn thing, man.

07:41.878 --> 07:43.504
-You didn't see no robbery?
-Nope.

07:43.504 --> 07:45.548
-Hear no gunshots?
-Uh-uh.

07:45.548 --> 07:48.801
Yes, you did, Lorenzo.
You saw Daddy Kool get robbed,
and you saw him shot.

07:48.801 --> 07:51.804
No, sir.
Just give me my summons.

07:51.804 --> 07:54.807
Lorenzo, now my shift
didn't even start yet,

07:54.807 --> 07:57.268
and three people already
insulted my intelligence--

07:57.268 --> 08:01.189
what occurred, what didn't occur
in this incident--plus one
tells me to kiss his ass.

08:01.189 --> 08:04.817
Now it's rollin' onto you.
Now we both know
that's not fair,

08:04.817 --> 08:07.361
but you're the one
up for the beating.

08:07.361 --> 08:10.156
-You should give up
what you saw, Lorenzo.
-Y-Y'all trying to get me hurt.

08:10.156 --> 08:12.825
You worry about now.
Let the future
take care of itself.

08:12.825 --> 08:15.244
We know you were out there
when this nonsense
went down, man.

08:17.955 --> 08:20.041
-Th-This all
in confidence, right?
-Absolutely.

08:25.922 --> 08:28.841
The shots went off--

08:28.841 --> 08:31.552
Daddy Kool and them
comin' out the Ibex, right?

08:31.552 --> 08:37.517
One of the boys get the car
and bring it around--
a Lexus 400 S.C.

08:37.517 --> 08:41.187
Then a dude with a pistol come
across the street. Bang, bang!
So I hit the pavement.

08:41.187 --> 08:44.440
The bodyguard backs off, the--
the thief takes his jewelry,

08:44.440 --> 08:46.567
and then he busts
some shots off, backs off,

08:46.567 --> 08:50.446
a-and... then just booked
across the street.
That--That was it.

08:51.614 --> 08:55.785
We're gonna need some
help with what this guy
looks like, Lorenzo.

08:55.785 --> 08:58.621
Word, I--
I-I didn't see him.

08:58.621 --> 09:01.207
-You didn't see this guy?
-Look, man, don't--
don't go grabbin' me again.

09:01.207 --> 09:03.376
I'm tellin' you,
I didn't see him
to say what he looked like.

09:09.423 --> 09:11.467
I-I got the plates
on his ride though.

09:18.474 --> 09:21.561
So this bookin'
across the street--
that wound up in a vehicle?

09:23.688 --> 09:25.940
You get a chance
later on, maybe you
can come back, Lorenzo.

09:25.940 --> 09:29.151
We'll get a reimbursement
of the time you lost
sellin' sausages.

09:29.151 --> 09:31.279
Man, cool.

09:39.537 --> 09:43.541
Maybe we get lucky off
the plate--get a mug shot for
the other victims to look at.

09:43.541 --> 09:48.838
Maybe we move that singer.
You reason with him,
I let him insult me.

09:53.050 --> 09:58.222
