up his bankroll, 600 bucks.

10:13.321 --> 10:15.656
What do the cops say?

10:15.656 --> 10:18.951
Jones--that the dealer
don't accuse--he had
nothin' to do with nothin'.

10:18.951 --> 10:21.829
-Does he back Szymanski?
-You know the other cop?

10:21.829 --> 10:26.000
-Yeah. Does Jones back
Szymanski?
-He backs him as
much as he saw.

10:26.000 --> 10:29.086
Says he was gone 90 seconds
to secure the radio car.

10:29.086 --> 10:31.547
-What does Szymanski say?
-Says he's set up.

10:31.547 --> 10:37.637
-By who?
-The dealer,
his partner, you.

10:37.637 --> 10:39.722
He says I set him up?

10:39.722 --> 10:42.516
He wasn't makin'
a lot of sense.

10:42.516 --> 10:46.062
-Will you keep me
posted on this?
-Absolutely.

11:05.581 --> 11:07.583
