wind up like Eddie Murphy
in that professor movie.

12:22.283 --> 12:25.161
Oh, that's where
I'm headed, James.
No question.

12:25.161 --> 12:27.580
That's, uh--
That's the road I'm on.

12:27.580 --> 12:31.083
