not to mess him up?
-Easy, Andy.

14:38.419 --> 14:41.297
-Have I been
disrespectful to you?
-SIPOWICZ: Nah, nah.

14:41.297 --> 14:44.425
Your big jerk client
handled that aspect
at the hospital.

14:44.425 --> 14:47.344
Okay. I wasn't there,
so I don't know
what got said first.

14:47.344 --> 14:49.889
I'm just here tryin' to address
the situation, that's all.

14:49.889 --> 14:50.806
Okay.

14:56.353 --> 14:58.314
